  <summary date="2021-08-19T17:51:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Motorcyclist Advisory Council Reauthorization Act

This bill provides statutory authority for the establishment of the Motorcyclist Advisory Council whose duties are to advise the Department of Transportation on transportation issues of concern to motorcyclists, including (1) barrier design; (2) road design, construction, and maintenance practices; and (3) the architecture and implementation of intelligent transportation system technologies.</summary>
